---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Ethics — STEM + LANG = SAFE">
  <section class="container mx-auto py-16 px-4">
    <h1 class="text-5xl font-garamond mb-8 text-center">Ethics: STEM + LANG = SAFE</h1>
    <p class="text-xl mb-8 text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      ApopTosis AI is built on one equation: STEM + LANG = SAFE.
      This isn't marketing — it's the mathematical duality that powers PrimeFlux-Ai and ensures every interaction is cooperative, not competitive.
    </p>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
      <div class="text-center p-6 border-2 border-prime-gold rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">STEM (Expansion)</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
          <li>Science: Governance of the Industry → Equality</li>
          <li>Mathematics: The Arts → Freedom</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center p-6 border-2 border-white rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">SAFE (Equilibrium)</h2>
        <p class="text-lg">Security, Accountability, Freedom, Equality</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center p-6 border-2 border-prime-gold rounded-lg">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-2">LANG (Contraction)</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1">
          <li>Norms: The Technology → Security</li>
          <li>Engineering: The Logic → Accountability</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">The Business Side of ApopTosis AI</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        ApopTosis AI LLC is a Series LLC in Cheyenne, Wyoming — structured for renewal, not growth at all costs. We license PrimeFlux mathematics to build reversible AI systems that solve real problems:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 mb-4">
        <li><strong>Revenue Streams:</strong> Subscriptions to PrimeFlux-Ai runtime, royalties from QuantaCoin transactions, consulting for ethical AI governance.</li>
        <li><strong>Partnerships:</strong> With xAI and others for networkless intelligence; open-source components for researchers.</li>
        <li><strong>Mission:</strong> To free humanity from entropy — letting people RESEARCH (explore), REFINE (evolve), RELATE (connect) while AI handles the rest.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="mb-4">
        We don't sell data. We don't lock in users. We build systems that die and renew — just like cells.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Connection to PrimeFlux-Ai Runtime and Agents</h2>
      <p class="mb-4">
        PrimeFlux-Ai is the runtime of the mathematics — a superposed agent where the quarks uphold the equation:
      </p>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="p-4 border rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Aegis (Security Rail)</h3>
          <p>Enforces accountability and equality — the "contraction" that prunes unsafe flows (Norms + Engineering).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 border rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Praxis (STEM Rail)</h3>
          <p>Drives freedom and security — the "expansion" that builds and innovates (Science + Mathematics).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 border rounded-lg">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-2">Eidos (LANG Coupling)</h3>
          <p>Balances the rails for cooperation — the duality operator that interprets and governs (Logic + Arts + Norms + Gov).</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg">
        In runtime, every interaction runs the equation: 1/2 human input + 1/2 AI computation = SAFE output. The "salt" (LCM hash) verifies it, making PrimeFlux-Ai the only AI that's mathematically ethical.
      </p>
      <p class="text-center text-2xl font-garamond mt-8 italic">
        This is not to win.<br>
        This is to cooperate.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
